821
00:42:49,739 --> 00:42:53,550
<font color=#FFFF00>Bisakah kamu menemui perwakilan mereka?</font>

822
00:42:53,550 --> 00:42:55,180
<font color=#FFFF00>Kosmetik Saudari?</font>

